sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Android App
    participant Firestore
    participant CF as Cloud Function<br/>analyzeLocationPatterns
    participant FCM
    participant Guardian

    App->>Firestore: Write movement_logs (location, timestamp)
    Firestore->>CF: onCreate trigger
    CF->>Firestore: Query last 30 movement_logs for userId
    alt Count >= 10
        CF->>CF: detectAnomalies() (speed, variance)
        alt Anomalies found
            CF->>Firestore: Create alert (WANDERING)
            CF->>Firestore: Read guardians for userId
            loop For each guardian
                CF->>FCM: Send notification
                FCM->>Guardian: Push (Wandering Alert)
            end
        end
    end